<template><section>
<h2 id="layout-bu-ju"><a class="header-anchor" href="#layout-bu-ju" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> Layout 布局</h2>
<p>通过基础的 24 分栏，迅速简便地创建布局。</p>
<h3 id="ji-chu-bu-ju"><a class="header-anchor" href="#ji-chu-bu-ju" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> 基础布局</h3>
